creator: ProTyme
descriptionHtml: This spoiler-free application is intended for players to use instead of the attack modifier deck and also allows the player to customise their deck as they wish. During game play the player can add curses/blessings and also keep track of their character using trackers for status effects, battle goals, health, and experience. In addition, the application also includes a handy reminder to shuffle once a crit or null card is drawn.
descriptionShort: A Gloomhaven companion deck that takes care of the attack modifier deck.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Large QoL patch. Jaws of the Lions Classes added soon. Any bugs or suggestions, feel free to contact me or leave a review.
*New first menu allows you to customise your deck using perks. Old menu can be accessed by clicking the deck icon next to class.
*Your game is now saved automatically when you close or minimize the app. You can resume the game by clicking resume on the main menu.
*Status effects now do things! Rolling modifiers now draws second card.
*You can now undo draws and shuffles.

Perk/QoL Update Hotfix:

*Three checkbox perks save correctly now.
*App won't save until you draw a card to help prevent accidental overwriting.
*Fixed a crash related to the Three Spears class and resuming.
*Disarm/Stun now check each other.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Patch Notes:
You can now go below 0 for -1 adjustment as requested limited by the number of them present in your deck.
Fixed an issue where -1 adjustment was being saved resulting in more -1s in your deck between sessions.
Switching classes now resets -1 adjustment.
Known Issues:
Reducing -1 adjustment then adjusting -1s through perks can make -1s go below 0. This will make the card count inaccurate but will go back to normal once you start the game.
